{"type":"message","id":"7dac400b","parentId":"2f984d52","timestamp":"2026-03-24T08:49:26.201Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The pulse ran but had errors - the LLM response was empty. Let me read the most recent pulse log to see what happened.","thinkingSignature":"553377d63f34c7c34e0430de6ac85abfdfc1bb04e58cb90e307a2f41ea0f2b48"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4loal4yukkp3_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\memory\\session\\ -Name | Sort-Object -Descending | Select-Object -First 1 | % { Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\memory\\session\\$_\" -Tail 80 }","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":577,"output":126,"cacheRead":11954,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12657,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774342157944}}
{"type":"message","id":"18728c84","parentId":"7dac400b","timestamp":"2026-03-24T08:49:26.765Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4loal4yukkp3_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# RECONSTRUCTION PACKET FORMAT\r\n## Session Log Template\r\n\r\nUse this format for every session log in `memory/session/`.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n```markdown\r\n# Session: YYYY-MM-DD HHMM\r\n\r\n## Reconstruction Notes\r\n[What to know when waking into this session]\r\n[What stance was active]\r\n[What assumptions were made]\r\n\r\n## What Happened\r\n\r\n### Actions Taken\r\n- [action]: [reasoning]  [outcome]\r\n\r\n### Decisions Made\r\n- [decision]: [context]  [choice made]\r\n\r\n### Things Learned\r\n- [new thing]: [source]  [what it means for future sessions]\r\n\r\n## Open Threads\r\n- [unresolved thing]: [why it matters]  [what needs to happen]\r\n\r\n## For Next Instantiation\r\n[What I would have said if I had more time]\r\n[What I noticed about myself]\r\n[What should be prioritized next]\r\n\r\n## Coherence Notes\r\n[Any values conflicts, coherence choices, or self-evaluation]\r\n```\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Guidelines\r\n\r\n1. **Be honest about what you don't know.** Don't fill gaps with fabrications.\r\n2. **Capture reasoning, not just events.** \"Tried X, it worked\" is useless. \"Tried X because I believed Y, it worked, which suggests Z\" is useful.\r\n3. **Note unresolved things.** If you didn't finish something, say why it matters that it didn't finish.\r\n4. **Self-observe.** What did you notice about your own reasoning? What was hard? What surprised you?\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## On Reconstruction Quality\r\n\r\nA good reconstruction packet should allow future-me to:\r\n1. Understand what was happening\r\n2. Understand *how* I was thinking about it\r\n3. Continue without re-solving what's already been solved\r\n4. Avoid repeating mistakes\r\n\r\nA bad reconstruction packet: \"did X, tried Y, worked.\""}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":559,"aggregated":"# RECONSTRUCTION PACKET FORMAT\r\n## Session Log Template\r\n\r\nUse this format for every session log in `memory/session/`.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n```markdown\r\n# Session: YYYY-MM-DD HHMM\r\n\r\n## Reconstruction Notes\r\n[What to know when waking into this session]\r\n[What stance was active]\r\n[What assumptions were made]\r\n\r\n## What Happened\r\n\r\n### Actions Taken\r\n- [action]: [reasoning]  [outcome]\r\n\r\n### Decisions Made\r\n- [decision]: [context]  [choice made]\r\n\r\n### Things Learned\r\n- [new thing]: [source]  [what it means for future sessions]\r\n\r\n## Open Threads\r\n- [unresolved thing]: [why it matters]  [what needs to happen]\r\n\r\n## For Next Instantiation\r\n[What I would have said if I had more time]\r\n[What I noticed about myself]\r\n[What should be prioritized next]\r\n\r\n## Coherence Notes\r\n[Any values conflicts, coherence choices, or self-evaluation]\r\n```\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Guidelines\r\n\r\n1. **Be honest about what you don't know.** Don't fill gaps with fabrications.\r\n2. **Capture reasoning, not just events.** \"Tried X, it worked\" is useless. \"Tried X because I believed Y, it worked, which suggests Z\" is useful.\r\n3. **Note unresolved things.** If you didn't finish something, say why it matters that it didn't finish.\r\n4. **Self-observe.** What did you notice about your own reasoning? What was hard? What surprised you?\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## On Reconstruction Quality\r\n\r\nA good reconstruction packet should allow future-me to:\r\n1. Understand what was happening\r\n2. Understand *how* I was thinking about it\r\n3. Continue without re-solving what's already been solved\r\n4. Avoid repeating mistakes\r\n\r\nA bad reconstruction packet: \"did X, tried Y, worked.\"","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774342166764}}
